{"tid":201383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人今晚有睇到東張西望⋯","createTime":"2017-04-14T16:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T06:43:41.000Z","uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d122769e9717df1b6aeaf4709416ed72a1a2e0a6","tid":201383,"uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"今晚講到條毛巾有啲一粒粒綠色嘅卵痴住係到毛巾到 又有一張蟲嘅圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果時係街食緊飯咁啱睇到 但係太嘈聽唔到佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重點係我前幾日掛係窗邊果條毛巾有呢啲嘢，我整走佢跟住照拎黎抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我宜家好驚，有冇巴打可以話俾我知果啲係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d25424baddf9df72e704f5462ae3741396fd9b","tid":201383,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"臭屁蟲蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8791858c0f34275bdc8d3c0560b6588c72b96b67","tid":201383,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"你今次大鑊啦"},{"pid":"73918f56af3c52cf7df0199535921b8402efceeb","tid":201383,"uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你今次大鑊啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咁白淨 我個身會唔會腐爛嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503ccc3997c1836a57d88676ba136bc0a438d36d","tid":201383,"uid":6051,"like":